I saw an angel with wings.

00:34:29.600 --> 00:34:31.570 align:middle line:84%
And I'm like, oh I've never
seen an angel with wings.

00:34:31.570 --> 00:34:33.800 align:middle line:84%
And I was taking
a walk in Seattle.

00:34:33.800 --> 00:34:35.657 align:middle line:84%
There's a lake
called Green Lake.

00:34:35.657 --> 00:34:36.790 align:middle line:84%
And I was walking
around the lake.

00:34:36.790 --> 00:34:38.620 align:middle line:84%
And I was thinking,
I really want

00:34:38.620 --> 00:34:39.909 align:middle line:90%
to see an angel with wings.

00:34:39.909 --> 00:34:41.540 align:middle line:84%
I really want to see
an angel with wings.

00:34:41.540 --> 00:34:43.520 align:middle line:84%
It was like a mantra
as I'm walking.

00:34:43.520 --> 00:34:46.770 align:middle line:84%
And this beautiful,
older black man,

00:34:46.770 --> 00:34:49.420 align:middle line:84%
