skating around me.

00:34:51.420 --> 00:34:55.639 align:middle line:84%
And then he was roller skating
in front of me backwards.

00:34:55.639 --> 00:34:56.870 align:middle line:90%
And he was laughing.

00:34:56.870 --> 00:34:59.290 align:middle line:84%
And he had these
beautiful, clear eyes.

00:34:59.290 --> 00:35:02.200 align:middle line:84%
And he said, I want
to tell you something.

00:35:02.200 --> 00:35:06.290 align:middle line:84%
The only thing that's
important is love of self,

00:35:06.290 --> 00:35:08.850 align:middle line:90%
love of others, and love of god.

00:35:08.850 --> 00:35:10.990 align:middle line:90%
Nothing else is important.

00:35:10.990 --> 00:35:15.730 align:middle line:84%
And it was almost as if
well-- then he skated off.

00:35:15.730 --> 00:35:16.930 align:middle line:84%
And I thought oh
my god, oh my god.

00:35:16.930 --> 00:35:17.629 align:middle line:90%
It was an angel.

00:35:17.629 --> 00:35:22.130 align:middle line:84%
And I thought, but I still want
to see an angel with wings.

00:35:22.130 --> 00:35:23.110 align:middle line:90%
But he was just saying--

00:35:23.110 --> 00:35:24.120 align:middle line:90%
What a message.

00:35:24.120 --> 00:35:24.820 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:35:24.820 --> 00:35:27.300 align:middle line:84%
It's not important whether you
see an angel with wings or not.

00:35:27.300 --> 00:35:29.160 align:middle line:90%
That's not what this is about.

00:35:29.160 --> 00:35:31.900 align:middle line:90%
What it's about is love.

00:35:31.900 --> 00:35:34.110 align:middle line:90%
And it sounds so cheesy.

00:35:34.110 --> 00:35:36.430 align:middle line:84%
But really that's
what it's about.

00:35:36.430 --> 00:35:39.550 align:middle line:90%
And love to me is acceptance.

00:35:39.550 --> 00:35:41.020 align:middle line:90%
Acceptance is love.

00:35:41.020 --> 00:35:45.290 align:middle line:84%
Love of self, accepting
yourself unconditionally.

